raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.1-4" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-sos
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/sos_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/sos/sos_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 37b5f8421791647ee92eec500c4163db59e4ed23f5ed5722f13313db2abd4861

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-brew
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-brew

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('sos')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('sos')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=sos
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Search contributed R packages, sort by package.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - brendanf
